At Pet Wellness Clinics we thrive on a fun, team-oriented and supportive environment where you will have the most current, state of the art, surgical and diagnostics tools and equipment available including digital dental x-ray, full digital radiology system, artificial intelligence (AI) reviews of every radiology case, therapy lasers, ultrasound, paperless medical record systems, complete in-house lab, and the list grows daily! 
Opportunities available: 
 Weekend Technician: EVERY Saturday, 7:45 AM – 12:30 PM (various locations) AND Sunday, 8:45 AM – 4:30 PM (Binford location in Indianapolis at 71st and Binford) 
Reasons to join: 
 Sign on bonus of $500 PLUS $500 incentive bonus opportunity after 3 months Competitive compensation Supportive work-life balance: NO after-hours emergencies Excellent mentoring and coaching through our highly skilled support team of Registered Vet Technicians, Surgery Technicians, Lead Technicians and Office Managers 
Qualifications: 
 Must be at least 18 years old High school diploma or GED; BS or RVT preferred 3+ months of hands-on experience within the veterinary industry through general practice, ER clinics, shelters, or through an RVT or pre-vet program Excellent reliability and dependability Ability to adapt to a fast-paced environment Strong problem-solving skills and attention to detail Ability to work with computers and electronic medical record system 
